People go traveling with map including related information as usual. Supported by mobile technology, GPS is used to navigate while traveling nowadays. This research presents the results of an analyze of traveling with mobile device and a completed construct travel agent system binding GPS with Google Map on Android platform. The innovative system helps people to plan their own traveling and get intimate service on independent travel. This system combining information technology and cultural creation is expected to promote Aboriginal Culture to attract people to go to the tribe, in addition to advance tourism industry vigorously.